alfresco5.1 installation from bin file >>>>>>>
wget https://sourceforge.net/projects/alfresco/files/alfresco-community-installer-201605-linux-x64.bin
chmod 777 alfresco-community-installer-201605-linux-x64.bin
./alfresco-community-installer-201605-linux-x64.bin

